vendor
*.sw[o-z]
*.out
out
# Built ob binary at the repo root, root-anchored so it doesn't match the
# cmd/ob source dir. The obu and obcrypt binaries need no entry: they share a
# name with a package directory (obu/, obcrypt/), so `go build` cannot write
# them at the root anyway; `go install` puts all binaries in GOPATH/bin and the
# CLI tests build to a temp dir.
/ob
